body:
#### PR description:
- New training files (UL16 and UL16APV) and configs are added for Pileup Jet Id (AK4CHS)
- New working points, same for both UL16 and UL16APV
- default `algo` is not changed as discussed before in earlier PR https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/32418

#### PR validation:
- Test with https://github.com/cms-data/RecoJets-JetProducers/pull/13

FYI: @alefisico @camclean @marinakolosova
title: [PUID] Add UL16 and UL16APV training configs
